\defgroup manip_func_reorder reorder

\brief Reorder an array according to the specified dimensions.

Exchanges data within an array such that the requested change in dimension
is satisfied. The linear ordering of data within the array is preserved.

\code
a [2 2 3 1]
    1.0000     3.0000
    2.0000     4.0000

    1.0000     3.0000
    2.0000     4.0000

    1.0000     3.0000
    2.0000     4.0000


reorder(a, 1, 0, 2) [2 2 3 1]  //equivalent to a transpose
    1.0000     2.0000
    3.0000     4.0000

    1.0000     2.0000
    3.0000     4.0000

    1.0000     2.0000
    3.0000     4.0000


reorder(a, 2, 0, 1) [3 2 2 1]
    1.0000     2.0000
    1.0000     2.0000
    1.0000     2.0000

    3.0000     4.0000
    3.0000     4.0000
    3.0000     4.0000
\endcode

\ingroup manip_mat
\ingroup arrayfire_func

=======================================================================

